comments: Sabonis (IND) is firming up and makes marginal contact with Huerter (ATL) as he disengage from the play.
Carter (ATL) makes marginal contact with Holiday's (IND) head while setting the pick.
Turner (IND) and Len (ATL) engage and separate during the rebound.
Carter (ATL) makes "high-five" contact with Warren (IND) after the release that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Len (ATL) places a resting hand against Sabonis' (IND) back and releases during the rebound.
Holiday (IND) places a collapsing arm against Young's (ATL) side as he veers into his path during his drive.
Warren (IND) makes slight contact to Young (ATL) body after the release that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
LLB shows Young (ATL) briefly grasps Holiday's (IND) arm during his drive.
Young (ATL) makes marginal contact to Holiday's (IND) arm  during his shooting motion that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Young (ATL) places a resting hand against Holiday's (IND) side and releases as his momentum is retreating during the drive.
Holiday (IND) moves into Len's (ATL) body and makes marginal contact with him as they disengage after the pick.
Turner (IND) makes hand on ball contact during Len's (ATL) upward shooting motion and dislodges the ball.
Young (ATL) makes contact to Holiday's (IND) body during his shooting motion that affects his driving shot attempt.
Warren (IND) and Young (ATL) make marginal hand to hand contact with one another off ball.
A correct 24 second violation is whistled at 00:19.8.
Sabonis (IND) has a hand against Carter's (ATL) side and removes it prior to his upward shooting motion.
Hunter (ATL) briefly places two hands against Warren's (IND) body off ball.
Holiday (IND) and Carter (ATL) make marginal contact with one another off ball during the screen.
Carter (ATL) hedges the screen and extends his arm against Holiday's (IND) head and affects his SQBR.
Carter (ATL) makes incidental contact with Holiday's (IND) foot at the top of his trajectory during his driving shot attempt.
Carter (ATL) makes contact with Warren's (IND) arm after he gathered the ball.
Warren (IND) commits a take foul on Young (ATL).
Holiday (IND) makes contact with Young's (ATL) arm as he gathers the inbound pass.
